{# packs/privacy-dsar/templates/verification-instructions.md.j2 #}
{# Sent to the requester to explain identity verification requirements. #}
Subject: Identity Verification Required — Privacy Request {{ request_id }}

Dear {{ requester_name | default('Privacy Rights Requester') }},

We have received your **{{ request_type | title }} Request** (reference: **{{ request_id }}**).

Before we can process your request, we are required to verify your identity to ensure
we release personal data only to the correct individual. This is a standard protection
required under applicable privacy law.

## Verification Method: {{ verification_method | replace('_', ' ') | title }}

{% if verification_method == 'email_link' %}
**Step 1:** Click the verification link below within 48 hours.

[Verify my identity]({{ verification_link }})

This link is single-use and expires at **{{ verification_expires_at | datetime('YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm UTC') }}**.

{% elif verification_method == 'knowledge_based' %}
**Step 1:** Answer the following questions to verify your identity.

Please reply to this email with answers to:
{% for q in knowledge_questions %}
- {{ q }}
{% endfor %}

{% elif verification_method == 'video_call' %}
**Step 1:** Schedule a brief identity verification call with our Privacy team.

[Book a verification call]({{ booking_link }})

The call takes approximately 10 minutes. Please have a government-issued photo ID available.

{% elif verification_method == 'notarized_id' %}
**Step 1:** Provide a notarized copy of a government-issued photo ID.

Please send the notarized copy to: {{ dpo_email }}
Subject line: "ID Verification — {{ request_id }}"

{% elif verification_method == 'signed_authorization' %}
**Step 1:** Provide a signed letter of authorization from the data subject you represent.

The letter must include the data subject's full name, their signature, and your name
as the authorized agent. Please send to: {{ dpo_email }}
Subject line: "Authorization — {{ request_id }}"

{% endif %}

## What Happens Next

Once your identity is verified, we will:
1. Map all personal data held about you across our systems.
2. {% if request_type == 'access' %}Prepare a complete data export for your review.
   {% elif request_type == 'portability' %}Prepare a machine-readable data export (JSON format).
   {% elif request_type == 'erasure' %}Prepare an erasure plan and confirm deletion.
   {% elif request_type == 'rectification' %}Document and process the corrections you requested.
   {% elif request_type == 'objection' %}Record your objection and restrict the relevant processing.
   {% endif %}
3. Obtain Data Protection Officer approval before any data is released.
4. Respond to you by **{{ deadline_at | date('MMMM D, YYYY') }}**.

If you did not submit this privacy request, please disregard this message and
contact {{ dpo_email }} to report it.

Regards,
{{ operator_name }} Privacy Team | {{ dpo_email }}
